data.description:
Get $200 off your first Month rent when you sign the lease by Feb 1, 2024. (Valid from 01/15/2024 till 01/31/2024)

Experience the perfect blend of comfort and convenience. Nestled in the heart of Grayslake, this home offers a unique opportunity to enjoy the best of suburban living.

Key Features:

Spacious Interiors: Boasting multiple bedrooms and bathrooms, this home is ideal for families or those who appreciate extra space. The open floor plan and corner lot ensures a bright and airy ambiance, perfect for relaxation and entertaining.

Modern Amenities: Equipped with state-of-the-art stainless Steel Frigidaire appliances, central heating, and air conditioning, this home merges modernity with comfort.

Outdoor Living: Enjoy the HOA maintained landscaped yard, perfect for outdoor activities or simply soaking in the tranquil surroundings. 4 Minutes away from Rollins Savanna Forest Preserve

Location Perks: Grayslake is known for its excellent schools, vibrant community, and abundant recreational activities. The property's location provides easy access to local shopping, dining, and entertainment options. 

Metra : 5 Minutes to Washington St & 7-Minutes to Round Lake beach Station

Safety and Community: Situated in a friendly and secure neighborhood, this home offers peace of mind and a sense of community.

Welcome to your potential new home! Below is a summary of the lease terms for this beautiful property in Grayslake, IL. Please review these terms carefully to ensure they align with your needs:

Lease Duration: The lease is offered for a standard term of 12 or 14 months, providing stability and comfort in your new home.

Monthly Rent: The rent is competitively priced for the area and amenities offered. Please contact us for the most current rate.

Renter's Insurance: Tenants are required to obtain renter's insurance to protect their personal belongings and liability.

Security Deposit: A security deposit, equivalent to one month's rent, is required at lease signing. This deposit is fully refundable, subject to the property's condition at the end of the lease term.

Utilities: Tenants are responsible for all utilities, including electricity, gas, water, sewer, and trash removal. Internet and cable services are not included but are available for setup by the tenant.

Pet Policy: Small pets are welcome! A small additional fee per pet is required, along with adherence to our HOA responsible pet ownership guidelines.

Maintenance and Repairs: Regular maintenance of the property is provided. Tenants are responsible for any damages caused by neglect or misuse.

Parking: 2 parking space is available, including a dedicated garage and driveway parking. Street Parking as per Village of Grayslake

Occupancy Limit: To maintain the quality of living and comply with local housing codes, there is a reasonable occupancy limit for the property.

Smoking Policy: This is a smoke-free property. Smoking is not permitted inside the home or on the premises.

Background and Credit Check: All potential tenants will undergo a background and credit check prior to lease approval.

Early Termination Clause: An early termination clause is included, subject to conditions outlined in the lease agreement.

We strive to make your rental experience pleasant and stress-free. For more information or to schedule a viewing, please contact us. We look forward to welcoming you to your new home
